  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774110/extras/fdce71bd81c844b8a84e864031ffab65.avif?t=1690746153\" width=610 height=105 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774110/extras/b62982dcff13bbe94cb55c9e0592fcd0.avif?t=1690746153\" width=610 height=104 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774110/extras/b0559760102094cebad34da485b0e2e6.avif?t=1690746153\" width=610 height=105 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774110/extras/e79c2eed9171a68a5bdaf2c2133e013b.avif?t=1690746153\" width=610 height=105 /></span><br>Escape Halloween Forest focuses on<strong> classic fun with a spooky twist!</strong> Collect all 5 gems to open a portal home.<strong> This short and casual game will get you in a festive mood! </strong>Collect pumpkins, travel through hedge mazes, leap across a forgotten swamp and more! Your adventure begins now with the perfect <strong>chills and thrills soundtrack </strong>to keep you company! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774110/extras/0aa3157023b11367c97326ce8b9c0d9b.poster.avif?t=1690746153\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774110/extras/0aa3157023b11367c97326ce8b9c0d9b.webm?t=1690746153\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774110/extras/0aa3157023b11367c97326ce8b9c0d9b.mp4?t=1690746153\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774110/extras/693840543fc25a22d1537cd6e2c5bdf5.poster.avif?t=1690746153\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774110/extras/693840543fc25a22d1537cd6e2c5bdf5.webm?t=1690746153\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774110/extras/693840543fc25a22d1537cd6e2c5bdf5.mp4?t=1690746153\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Gameplay Time: 1-3 hours<br></li><li> Over 12 thematic spooky music tracks<br></li><li> 7 different characters to help<br></li><li> Comical wholesome fun</li></ul>",
